This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) because it deals with natural language processing and machine translation. It could also belong to cs.SE (Software Engineering) because it deals with program comprehension and software maintenance. Additionally, it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) because it uses neural models for generating natural language summaries. Finally, it could belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) because it deals with summarization of program subroutines.
